snippet.title: Render96 2.1 Trailer! (Bowser Update!)
snippet.description:
The Render96 2.1 Trailer is here! 
If you want to be a concept artist / mid poly 3d artist for the team apply here! https://forms.gle/zB63HGpEDH6guFiT8
Check below for proper credits!
